%% Diagram: Component Composition Primitives Map
%% Type: flowchart
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
flowchart TB
    Q{What are you<br/>composing?}

    Q -->|Same component shape,<br/>different content| PROPS["Props + children<br/>(static composition)"]
    Q -->|One parent, many<br/>related children| COMPOUND["Compound components<br/>(shared state via Context)"]
    Q -->|Behaviour without UI| HEADLESS["Hooks / Headless components<br/>(Radix, Headless UI, React Aria)"]
    Q -->|Same behaviour,<br/>different rendering| RENDER["Render props /<br/>function-as-children"]
    Q -->|Cross-cutting service<br/>or DI| CTX["Context provider<br/>(SDK injection)"]
    Q -->|Wrap many components<br/>with the same chrome| HOC["Higher-order component<br/>(legacy; prefer hooks)"]

    PROPS --> EX1["Card title prop<br/>Layout children"]
    COMPOUND --> EX2["Tabs.List / Tabs.Panel<br/>Menu.Item / Select.Option"]
    HEADLESS --> EX3["useCombobox()<br/>Dialog.Root / Dialog.Trigger"]
    RENDER --> EX4["Virtualised list<br/>FormField render={...}"]
    CTX --> EX5["SdkProvider<br/>ThemeProvider"]
    HOC --> EX6["withErrorBoundary<br/>(rare; hook variant preferred)"]

    classDef question fill:#3D3D3D,stroke:#1F1F1F,color:#fff
    classDef pattern fill:#2E5A88,stroke:#1F4870,color:#fff
    classDef example fill:#1F6E68,stroke:#155752,color:#fff
    classDef legacy fill:#7A4A2D,stroke:#5A3520,color:#fff
    class Q question
    class PROPS,COMPOUND,HEADLESS,RENDER,CTX pattern
    class HOC legacy
    class EX1,EX2,EX3,EX4,EX5,EX6 example
